Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.60,0:00:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini, cuaca cerah\Nmenyelimuti seluruh Amerika Serikat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal kami prediksi minggu ini akan buruk,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.44,0:00:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mohon maaf prediksi kami meleset jauh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.89,0:00:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meryl, jangan mulai yang aneh-aneh lagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.66,0:00:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, hati-hati saat menjemur pakaian.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Angin masih bertiup kencang.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.18,0:00:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Angin yang berembus hari itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.26,0:00:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dampak apa yang dibawanya pada dunia\Npasca-pertempuran besar ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami akan terus sampaikan\Nlaporan cuaca selanjutnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, tolong bawa itu ke sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, rumahnya sudah jadi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.39,0:02:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat sekali, seperti jamur!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seminggu telah berlalu sejak saat itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.83,0:02:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pemulihan pasca-perang Jaku\Nyang sempat macet, kini melesat cepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Usai perang, bantuan dari Amerika\Ndan negara lain terus mengalir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melihat perjuangan mereka,\Nkami tak bisa diam saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.46,0:02:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami dapat cetak biru dari badan pemeriksa,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi ayo bangun bagian\Nyang bisa dibangun dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.96,0:02:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, ayo mulai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.83,0:02:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebelum era Quirk,\Npemulihan sebesar ini butuh sepuluh tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi dengan banyaknya Quirk yang berkumpul,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pasti cepat selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak bisa kembali seperti semula.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kujelaskan sebelum operasi,\Nini hasil terbaik.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami semua melihat pencapaiannya,\Njadi kami berupaya semampu kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami sambung ulang\Nberkali-kali agar bentuknya utuh,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi tak ada jaminan bisa gerak\Nmeski direhabilitasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Demi kelanjutan aktivitas pahlawan,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pilihan pakai prostetik\Nseperti Mirko juga ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.46,0:03:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak perlu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Quirk-ku berasal dari telapak tangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.26,0:03:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, dia bahkan\Ntak punya apa-apa sejak awal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rehabilitasi sekeras apa pun akan kujalani!\NMulai sekarang!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak. Kau hanya boleh\Nlatihan ringan saat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masalah utamamu bukan tangan, tapi jantung.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tanpa teknik gila Edgeshot\Nyang meresusitasi jantung dan parumu,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau pasti sudah mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bahkan tak paham bagaimana\Nkau bisa bertarung sejauh itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.08,0:04:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan jalan berkilo-kilometer setelahnya\Njuga tak masuk akal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau diberi hidup dan kau menyambutnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pokoknya, kau harus istirahat total.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.93,0:04:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah sadar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak kusangka\Nakan sekamar denganmu, All Might.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu permintaan Tsukauchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.53,0:04:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lebih mudah dijaga,\Ndan kamar rumah sakit juga terbatas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}All Might, tubuhmu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya ini pertama kalinya\Nmereka pasang baut sebanyak ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana denganmu, Midoriya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mulai merasakan kembali tanganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.90,0:04:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku gagal menyelamatkan nyawa Tenko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.53,0:05:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski kusentuh hatinya\Ndan kuhancurkan bencinya,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tenko tetap pemimpin\NLiga Penjahat hingga akhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagai orang yang pernah hampir mati...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutku yang penting adalah\Nekspresi yang ia tunjukkan di akhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah menghancurkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tergantung pada apa\Nyang kalian lakukan besok.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lakukan yang terbaik.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau di akhir bocah\Nyang menangis itu tiada,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.76,0:05:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}maka aku yakin\Nkau telah menyelamatkan hatinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekaligus menuntaskan misi One For All.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.37,0:05:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pindahkan Quirk-nya, 'kan?\NAku bisa merasakannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku masih rasakan\Nsedikit sisa bara terakhirnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kok kau masih bisa bergerak?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kacchan! Syukurlah kau selamat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, All Might.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak ini ternyata\Nsangat khawatirkan kondisimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.14,0:06:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf juga ya, Izuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, barusan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bara terakhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.07,0:06:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi tanpa Quirk lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Lagi pula, awalnya aku memang tak punya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi tak ada yang perlu disesali.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.50,0:06:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya seperti diberi\Nkesempatan bermimpi indah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pakai trik licik apa biar bisa lolos, hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu aku akan terbang lebih tinggi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.19,0:06:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus terus bertumbuh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Awas kalau kau\Nbiarkan aku menyalipmu, Izuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kacchan menangis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak... mau...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudku...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.33,0:07:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang sebenarnya telah\Nkulakukan padamu selama ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah kenapa, kurasa kita\Nakan terus bersaing selamanya...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengejar satu sama lain,\Naku selalu berasumsi begitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hentikan, itu enggak banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, aku masih punya bara terakhir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tubuhku lemah, mental jadi ikut goyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian berdua sudah tumbuh begitu kuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.31,0:07:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian banyak berubah\Nsejak hari pertama kita bertemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari itu, saat Midoriya mulai berlari...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagiku, dialah pahlawan terbaik.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kini, dia menggerakkan semua orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia jadi pahlawan terbaik bagi semua orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan kau yang memberiku waktu\Nuntuk sampaikan ini padanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau, Nak Bakugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau juga pahlawan terbaik.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.74,0:08:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sungguh terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.86,0:08:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Waktu kecil,\Nkupikir begitu pertarungan berakhir,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dunia otomatis jadi damai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi cerita kami belum bisa berakhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Usai pertempuran,\Nsampai kami bisa tunjukkan masa depan cerah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami harus terus melangkah lebih jauh lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Juni. Upacara kelulusan senior\Nyang tertunda akhirnya digelar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:09:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kentang, mereka semua cuma kentang...\N- Selamat! Kalian semua sudah berjuang luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.53,0:09:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lulus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.38,0:09:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami bakal rindu Senior Nejire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf ya, upacara kelulusannya telat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.66,0:09:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sakura sudah gugur, tapi setidaknya\Nayo buat perpisahan ini meriah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini sama sekali bukan suasana kelulusan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah harusnya ini acara sedih?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya seperti festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Uwah Nejire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.93,0:09:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lukamu tidak sakit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sakit sih, tapi kalau senang,\Nrasanya hilang! Aneh, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.54,0:09:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu berkat Mirio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia terus menjaga kita\Nwaktu kita tumbang karena Peti Langit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permintaan kebutuhan penting\Ndari berbagai negara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rencana pemulihan,\Nhitungan biaya dan pengadaannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.06,0:09:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penempatan dan distribusi bantuan,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}memastikan ketersediaan tempat\Ntidur rumah sakit, dukungan medis...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.73,0:10:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagi masyarakat super pun,\Npemulihan secepat ini pasti karena
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ada upaya tokoh besar dunia,\NKepala Sekolah Nezu,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Naikkan BPM-nya sedikit lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Hah! Gampang banget ngomongnya.\N- yang melakukan pendekatan ke berbagai negara.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kepala sekolah sudah selalu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.56,0:10:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}melihat apa yang terjadi pasca-pertarungan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lirik yang bagus! Mewakili U.A.,\Nangkat tanganmu untuk Fuwa Mawata!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kayak rap battle! Keren banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keren?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.11,0:10:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku yang aneh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo rap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.49,0:10:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Togata Mirio!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak telah hadir\Ndi upacara kami hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kok jadi pidato serius, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita kehilangan banyak hal,\Ntanpa dapat apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertarungan pahlawan biasanya\Ncuma soal mengembalikan minus ke nol.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jurusan umum, support, bisnis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:11:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita semua, gunakan ilmu yang kita\Npelajari di sini untuk berjuang bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kita masih belum kembalikan semuanya\Nke titik nol.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiga tahun kami\Ndemi masa depan setelah ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.13,0:11:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini bukanlah garis finis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dunia tanpa humor\Ntak punya masa depan cerah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.91,0:11:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dunia di mana banyak orang tersenyum\Ndan hidup positif.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itulah garis finis kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.10,0:11:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Togata...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat aku, Nighteye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita! Mulai dari hari ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Para adik kelas!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai jumpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.53,0:11:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya ini tradisi kelulusan U.A.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan kemudian...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biasanya wali kelas tak lanjut\Nke tahun berikutnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi yah, situasinya begini.\NJadi setahun lagi kita bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Senang kami masih bersamamu, Pak Aizawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau menangis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kami tak ingin orang lain selain Pak Aizawa!\N- Kurasa ini semua sudah berakhir sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah kau harusnya di rumah sakit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.56,0:12:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya asal aku diam, tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan aku harus ada saat semua orang hadir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.36,0:12:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alasan yang cukup normal\Nuntuk orang sepertimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ingat, kau harus diam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masuklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Izinkan aku ucapkan adieu lagi!\NAku keluar dari U.A.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aoyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aoyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.53,0:12:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tekadmu belum berubah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal berkatmu\Nkita bisa pecah pasukan All For One!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Para guru dan Tsukauchi bilang\Naku boleh tinggal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku ingin menutup semuanya\Ndengan tuntas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.54,0:12:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena masukku ke sini\Nterlibat rencana All For One,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa sambut kelulusan\Nseperti hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.28,0:12:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan tebus dosaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.32,0:12:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu kembali mengejar jalan pahlawan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku baik-baik saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.26,0:13:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku sudah genggam tangan kalian!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suatu hari nanti, pasti...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan berdiri bangga\Ndi samping kalian semua!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.05,0:13:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aoyama, kau...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.13,0:13:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau benar-benar paling jantan\Ndibanding yang lain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan menangis, semuanya!\NAku benci suasana murung!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silau banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kontrolnya makin presisi\Ndibanding festival budaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena itu di sini ada kejutan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.29,0:13:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anggota baru Kelas A!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Susah masuk kayak gini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.86,0:13:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shinso!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya kau masuk Kelas A!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia pindah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masuk Kelas A!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gila, lisensi sementaramu\Nsudah resmi keluar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang, Shinso.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini saat yang tepat\Nbuat bahas pesta perpisahanku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.16,0:13:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Apa tidak tepat?! Tidak tepat, ya?!\N- Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aoyama, hentikan! Berhenti!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:13:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Quirk-ku masih bermasalah!\NSemuanya melihatku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:13:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, wajah aslinya! Imut banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan lihat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dewi itu sudah ada di sana sejak dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.21,0:14:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei. Masih ada pengumuman lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.76,0:14:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sementara waktu,\Nmurid Jurusan Pahlawan tahun 2 dan 3
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akan ditugaskan ke daerah terdampak\Nuntuk rekonstruksi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku perwakilan sekaligus pimpinan lapangannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.36,0:14:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain pemulihan yang sedang berjalan,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kita akan keliling seluruh negeri\Ndemi mencegah keamanan memburuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti setelah pensiunnya All Might\Ndan tentu saja pasca-perang Jaku,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}setelah pertempuran besar\Nyang layak masuk buku sejarah,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}selalu ada kekacauan\Nyang tak tercatat di buku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dunia tanpa Simbol Perdamaian.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.70,0:14:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}All For One juga lahir\Ndari kekacauan seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke? Erasen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.96,0:14:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Erasen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, aku dulu murid kelas Eraser juga, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.06,0:14:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian tak dikeluarkan 'kan?\NEnak banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Membiarkan anak manja seperti kami\Nrasakan "kematian" sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.92,0:15:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seram sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Fuwa, sudah cukup. Pergi sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}berkat itu, aku akhirnya tahu\Nuntuk apa aku ingin jadi pahlawan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai jumpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, murid baru, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulai besok kita jadi senior, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya berjalan sangat cepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.42,0:15:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulai besok kita akan sibuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, kita punya waktu istirahat juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sero, berhenti menyindirku terus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tidak baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.82,0:15:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan begitu! Kupikir itu keren!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.59,0:15:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Uraraka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Deku juga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, dicukur karena cedera, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.06,0:15:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semoga cepat tumbuh lagi, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau soal ganti gaya... Tokoyami?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.73,0:15:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak. Tapi aku suka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, begitu. Jadi kau suka, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Midoriya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.49,0:16:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Todoroki, kau bisa datang\Nke pesta perpisahan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau bukan hari ini, kapan saja bisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, aku sampai sini saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Todoroki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.90,0:16:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.66,0:16:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal kubilang kau tak perlu datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.46,0:16:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kau bilang begitu,\Nkalian juga sama, Fuyumi, Natsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, Ibu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kau bilang begitu, kau juga sama, Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku datang bukan karena wajib.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian juga begitu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berbicara masih memungkinkan,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi hanya beberapa menit per hari.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menuju kematian dengan tenang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:17:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itulah kondisi Todoroki Toya saat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Datang berbondong-bondong...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bukan tempat wisata.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.02,0:17:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Toya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami datang bicara soal masa depan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Toya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pensiun sebagai pahlawan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak awal aku memang\Nberniat pensiun usai perang,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi sekarang berdiri saja aku tak mampu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pahlawan Endeavor sudah hangus dan mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Api milikmu jauh lebih kuat\Ndaripada siapa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, begitu, ya. Turut berduka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan sok manis\Nsetelah semua yang terjadi, pengecut...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Toya paling tahu tentang aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mengamatiku terus, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau ingin aku melihatmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku tak melihatmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa pun kata orang,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}panasmu itu adalah Hellflame-ku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiap hari aku tonton video pengakuanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah, lihat sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulai sekarang...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku datang tiap hari. Ayo bicara.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memang terlambat,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.96,0:18:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi mari bicara.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Detak jantungnya meningkat,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ini akan membebani tubuhnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rei, Natsuo,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.91,0:18:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fuyumi, Shoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.62,0:18:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan waktu yang kalian berikan,\Nmari kita bicara.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau benci aku, katakan saja,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.56,0:19:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apa pun itu, luapkan padaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kak Toya, aku juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada banyak hal yang ingin kubicarakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita sudahi untuk hari ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Besok saja...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, boleh tanya satu hal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.96,0:19:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada sesuatu yang ingin kutanyakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.93,0:19:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kak Toya, makanan kesukaanmu apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tenaganya sudah habis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini kita buat dia tidur, besok lagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soba.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.06,0:19:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama sepertiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.90,0:19:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begini terus, kita cuma jalan paralel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harus bersinggungan. Meski terpaksa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.56,0:20:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai sini saja buatku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.22,0:20:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, perasaanku tak berubah.\NAku tak mau terlibat lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau menikah sama pacarku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada upacara.\NAku juga tak bakal kenalkan dia ke kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.66,0:20:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.67,0:20:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana denganmu, Kak?\NKau sudah berhenti kerja, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.40,0:20:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi ibu salah satu muridku\Nkenalkan aku ke tempat kerja baru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya mau bantu aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.36,0:20:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jujur saja,\Nkita sudah jalankan tanggung jawab.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah menerima hukuman juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukannya ini sudah cukup?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.37,0:20:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan terus tebus dosaku, seumur hidupku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian tak perlu melihatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Percikan api yang kena kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebisa mungkin kuterima semua.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika hidupku masih punya arti,\Nhanya itulah satu-satunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu neraka, tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.88,0:21:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku dapat undangan untuk berdansa tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.86,0:21:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baru kali ini, kurasa ayah keren.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shoto bagaimana? Balik sekolah, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.36,0:21:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Naik mobilku saja. Kakak juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah, Ibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku punya teman-teman Kelas A,\Njadi aku baik-baik saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.89,0:21:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa menjadi orang yang kuinginkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.82,0:21:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat amat baliknya!\NKau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.60,0:22:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lapar. Ayo makan daging.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.02,0:22:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bodoh! Bilang yang lebih semangat, dong!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Neraka, tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.66,0:22:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang melihat kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.36,0:22:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tegar sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.53,0:22:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana ini akan berubah?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.91,0:22:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau bagaimana kita akan mengubahnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.30,0:22:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, halo, Mera?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.66,0:22:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini Hawks,\NKetua Komisi Keamanan Publik yang baru.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.46,0:23:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Episode selanjutnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.29,0:23:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertarungan panjang akhirnya usai.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.35,0:23:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, usai laga, duka selalu menyertai.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.38,0:23:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu adalah rasa sakit\Ndari nyawa yang hilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.18,0:23:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luka kehilangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.39,0:23:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuingin ulurkan tangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.85,0:23:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk menyertaimu dalam duka itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.36,0:23:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Agar hatimu terasa sedikit lebih ringan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.73,0:23:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selanjutnya, "Gadis yang Suka Tersenyum".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.98,0:23:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski mungkin dianggap ikut campur.
